33a. No parenthesis. This was all on the banners (I have seen that film).

33b. Eliminate this "shown", please.

34. This insertion is impossible. Nothing should be added here. I worked for a month on this passage.

35. No date, please!

36. I have rearranged this.





TO: JASON EPSTEIN

CC, 1 p.





Goldwin Smith Hall

